\N<Luna>*pant*... *pant*... With this, I've defeated all the mid-
boss monsters in the Tower Dungeon! Mid-bosses are supposed
to be really strong, but I managed to do it even without
\N[2]-kun...

\N<Luna>It seems I've leveled up more than I thought, thanks to this
dungeon♪ But I definitely shouldn't underestimate the final
boss; it's better to challenge it with two people rather
than alone.

\N<Luna>The next challenge will be the climax of conquering this
dungeon... I'm getting really nervous... Let's make sure
we're fully prepared with plenty of items, the best
preparation we've ever had!

\N<\N[2]>*pant*... *pant*... Yes! Yes! Yes! With this, all the mid-
bosses have been defeated♪ No matter what kind of monster it
is, I've leveled up enough to defeat them on my own!

\N<\N[2]>I've been desperately hunting monsters to pay off my debt,
but it seems I've not only earned money but also leveled up
enough to gain confidence...

\N<\N[2]>That being said... It seems reckless to challenge the final
boss alone, so it's safer to rely on Luna-chan's strength...
Alright, the big payday is just ahead, let's prepare
thoroughly and take it on!

\N<\N[2]>*pant*... *pant*... Victory over an incredible monster! With
this, I've managed to defeat all the mid-bosses in the Tower
Dungeon--♪

\N<Luna>Yay～♪ We've finally made it to the last big battle! All the
effort we put into defeating so many monsters has paid off～

\N<\N[2]>That's right, we've been steadily leveling up and we've
become quite strong... I'm feeling confident, next is the
final boss battle... We'll definitely defeat it and end our
journey!

\N<Luna>Now that we've come this far, I want to end on a success♪
Let's make sure we're fully prepared with plenty of items,
the best preparation we've ever had!

\N<Luna>*pant*... *pant*... I was able to defeat the strongest
monster so far～... Dalton-san, I can't thank you enough for
all your help... Thank you so much.

\N<Dalton>There's no need for formalities～～ We trust each other enough
to defeat even a mid-boss like this. Our experiences
together and our "relationship" as a man and a woman have
truly paid off.

\N<Luna>Yes... There's been a lot, but certainly as Dalton-san says.
Without our perfect harmony in attack, we wouldn't have been
able to defeat such a formidable foe.

\N<Dalton>Mhm mhm♪ I'm glad Luna-chan has realized it too. We are
already inseparable "partners"!

\N<Dalton>So here's a proposal～... After we defeat the final boss, how
about you break off your relationship with \N[2]-kun and
start dating "me"?
\N<Luna>Eh?! Th-that is...

\N<Dalton>I've really enjoyed adventuring with Luna-chan～ And seeing
you fight so lively, and now being able to share joy
together like this, I want to cherish this relationship♪

\N<Dalton>You don't have to answer right now♪ I just wanted to convey
my honest feelings. After we defeat the final boss, please
let me hear what Luna-chan feels♪

\N<Luna>...I understand...(Ugh... why am I feeling so shaken? My
answer should be clear.)

\N<Dalton>(Good good, she didn't reject me outright like before – she
must be confused about cutting ties with \N[2]. Heh heh heh～)

\N<Luna>*pant*... *pant*... I was able to defeat the strongest
monster so far～... Bob-san, I can't thank you enough for all
your help... Thank you so much.

\N<Bob>No problem～～♪ No matter what kind of mid-boss it is, when
they face our strongest pair they're done for. The memories
and sexual relationship we've shared so far are special
indeed♪

\N<Luna>Yes... There's been a lot, but my dungeon conquests were
adventures with Bob-san. Without our perfect harmony in
attack, we wouldn't have been able to defeat such a
formidable foe.

\N<Bob>Since Luna and I are so compatible both in heart and body, I
want us to become an official "couple" and continue
adventuring together. Is that okay? I'm serious here!
\N<Luna>Eh?! Th-that is...

\N<Bob>You don't have to answer right now♪ After we defeat the last
boss, please let me hear what Luna feels! I'll be waiting
for a good response～♪

\N<Luna>...I understand...(Ugh... why am I feeling so shaken? My
answer should be clear.)

\N<Bob>(Good～♪ It seems there's a choice to break up with her
boyfriend～ Can't wait for her to dump him and for me to have
Luna all to myself～♪)

\N<Luna>*pant*... *pant*... I was able to defeat the strongest
monster so far～... Arashi-san, I can't thank you enough for
all your help... Thank you so much.

\N<Arashi>That's right, when you really like someone you go all out
for them♪

\N<Arashi>Thanks to all the skinship we've had up until now, our
breathing was in sync and Luna-chan's movements were perfect
– that was definitely a factor in our victory～♪

\N<Luna>Yes... There's been a lot, but maybe Arashi-san is right...
Without our perfect harmony in attack, we wouldn't have been
able to defeat such a formidable foe.

\N<Arashi>Right? We're such an awesome combo that we realized it while
conquering dungeons. I've never met anyone else with such
good chemistry before – feels like fate man.

\N<Arashi>If we say goodbye after defeating the final boss, I think
I'd regret it for life～ So how about it... Will you
seriously "go out" with me? Let's aim to be high-level
adventurers together?
\N<Luna>Eh?! Th-that is...

\N<Arashi>Up until now your boyfriend might have been number one
but... After going through hell together like this, let's
aim for higher as adventurers, shall we?

\N<Arashi>I'll ask for your answer another time♪ I'm seriously serious
about this～～ So think about it seriously and let me know how
Luna-chan feels～♪

\N<Luna>...I understand...(Ugh... why am I feeling so shaken? My
answer should be clear.)

\N<Arashi>(Yes! If she's considering it, that means there's a chance
she'll choose me, right? Just a little more and the busty
beauty will be all mine♪ Heh heh heh...)

\N<Luna>*pant*... *pant*... We were able to defeat the strongest
monster so far～... Syouta-kun, I can't thank you enough for
all your help... Thank you so much.

\N<Syouta>Heh heh heh～～ Being thanked by my disciple sure feels good♪
It was worth going all out for the first time in a while♪

\N<Syouta>Well, my performance was one thing, but～～ "the disciple's
performance" was also pretty impressive. Thanks to our past
experiences, we were able to launch perfectly synchronized
attacks, and it was electrifying～♪

\N<Luna>That's true... There's been a lot, but without our perfect
harmony in attack, we wouldn't have been able to defeat such
a formidable foe...

\N<Syouta>Finally realized it, huh?～～ That's right, we're the best
disciple-master pair♪ The results prove it after all♪

\N<Syouta>Speaking of which, I've been wondering... What are you going
to do after we defeat the final boss? You're going to stay
on this island and continue adventuring as my disciple,
right?
\N<Luna>Eh?! Th-that is...

\N<Syouta>What's there to hesitate about with such an unbeatable pair
like us～～ Can't be helped... I'll give you some time, so
make sure to let me hear your answer by the time we defeat
the last boss!!

\N<Luna>...I understand...(Ugh... why am I feeling so shaken? My
answer should be clear.)

\N<Syouta>(It's not fun that she didn't answer right away... But if
she's hesitating, that means there's a chance she'll stay on
the island～～ Well, that's fine♪)
